&lt;p&gt;Our CEO began his tech career as an SDR and that experience has shaped how we invest in this team.&amp;nbsp; We see SDRs as future sales leaders and provide a clear path to growth into an Account Executive role.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
